{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 55,
  "title": "第五十五章（含德）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "含德之厚者，比於赤子："
    },
    {
      "text": "蜂蠆虺蛇弗螫。"
    },
    {
      "text": "攫鳥猛獸弗搏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "骨弱筋柔而握固。"
    },
    {
      "text": "未知牝牡之合而朘怒，精之至也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "終日號而不嚘，和之至也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "和曰常。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知和曰明。"
    },
    {
      "text": "益生曰祥。"
    },
    {
      "text": "心使氣曰強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "物壯即老，謂之不道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不道早已。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "神明保佑含德之人，若父母之於赤子也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "蜂蠇蛇虺不螫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子不害於物，物亦不害之。故太平之世，人無貴賤，仁心，有刺之物，還返其本，有毒之蟲，不傷於人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子筋骨柔弱而持物堅固，以其意心不移也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子未知男女會合而陰陽作怒者，由精氣多之所致也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子從朝至暮啼號聲不變易者，和氣多之所至也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能和氣柔弱有益於人者，則為知道之常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能知道之常行，則日以明達於玄妙也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "祥，長也。言益生欲自生，日以長大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "心當專一和柔而神氣實內，故形柔。而反使妄有所為，和氣去於中，故形體日以剛強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "萬物壯極則枯老也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "枯老則不得道矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不得道者早死。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子無求無欲，不犯眾物，故毒蟲之物無犯之人也。含德之厚者，不犯於物，故無物以損其全也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以柔弱之故，故握能周固。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "作，長也。無物以損其身，故能全長也。言含德之厚者，無物可以損其德、渝其真，柔弱不爭而不摧折，皆若此也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無爭欲之心，故終日出聲而不嗄也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "物以和為常，故知和則得常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不皦不昧，不溫不涼，此常也。無形不可得而見，曰明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "生不可益，益之則夭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "心宜無有，使氣則強。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
